00:26:22,873 --> 00:26:23,707
Good to see you.

426
00:27:00,494 --> 00:27:01,662
 Come on, Diane.

427
00:27:01,662 --> 00:27:02,538
Time to introduce
the man himself.

428
00:27:09,586 --> 00:27:12,089
Oh my god, Diane McGowin
