 Hello?

444
00:28:48,894 --> 00:28:54,858
 Is this 555-0196?

445
00:28:54,858 --> 00:28:57,444
 Yeah, mom?

446
00:28:57,444 --> 00:28:58,195
 Who is this?

447
00:29:01,823 --> 00:29:03,367
 So what happened?

448
00:29:03,367 --> 00:29:05,827
 Well, I got there
and Jimmy was there.

449
00:29:05,827 --> 00:29:09,373
And mom said she was OK but
she was really freaked out.

450
00:29:09,373 --> 00:29:10,582
 Did she know who you were?

451
00:29:10,582 --> 00:29:11,750
 Yeah, of course
she knew who I was.

452
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,043
 What happened at the thing?

453
00:29:13,043 --> 00:29:14,795
Why'd she call you
in the first place?

454
00:29:14,795 --> 00:29:16,588
 Well, Ginny says that she like
froze on stage, on the podium.

455
00:29:16,588 --> 00:29:19,007
JACK: You mean,
like, stage fright?

456
00:29:19,007 --> 00:29:22,886
 Yeah, and then she ran out,
like right through the crowd.

457
00:29:22,886 --> 00:29:24,596
JACK: She just ran away?

458
00:29:24,596 --> 00:29:25,847
 Yeah.

459
00:29:25,847 --> 00:29:27,474
JACK: Did she talk
about [INAUDIBLE?

460
00:29:27,474 --> 00:29:28,684
 No, she didn't.

461
00:29:28,684 --> 00:29:29,851
You know Mom.
