00:29:31,269 --> 00:29:32,980
But she didn't talk at all.

464
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:35,315
JACK: Did you tell her you knew?

465
00:29:35,315 --> 00:29:36,358
 I didn't what to say.

466
00:29:36,358 --> 00:29:38,235
She wouldn't talk about it.

467
00:29:38,235 --> 00:29:40,404
 She was-- she was
quiet the whole way home.

468
00:29:40,404 --> 00:29:42,489
JACK: You guys haven't seen her
taking any pills or anything,

